    - updated README to reflect Logstash 1.4.0 support.
    # inputs
    - fixed plugin to locate vendor logstash jars prior to importing jruby-kafka
    # outputs
    - fixed plugin to locate vendor logstash jars prior to importing jruby-kafka
0.4.1 (April 8, 2014)
